      <body>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" subtype="diplomatic" xml:id="hafa0001.diplomatic" corresp="#hafa0001.transcription #hafa0001.translation">
            <p>ΑΓΙ<lb/>
                    +<lb/>
                    ΟΣ  Α  Ω<lb/>
                    ΚΣ
                </p>
         </div>
         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" subtype="transcription" xml:id="hafa0001.transcription" corresp="#hafa0001.diplomatic #hafa0001.translation">
            <p>Ἅγι<lb/>
                    ος <lb/>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>Κ</abbr>
                  <ex>ύριο</ex>
                  <abbr>ς</abbr>
               </expan>
               <lb/>
                    Α Ω
                </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="hafa0001.translation" corresp="#hafa0001.diplomatic #hafa0001.transcription">
            <p>Holy Lord...</p>
         </div>
      </body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>This inscription recalls Isaiah 6:3. Presumably it continued to the right of the encircled cross, which is cut in relief. Dimensions refer to entire remainder of stone.</p>
         </div>
